Class AdjacencyListGraph<V>

java.lang.Object
pagerank.datastructure.graph.AdjacencyListGraph<V>
Type Parameters:
V - the type of vertices in the graph.
All Implemented Interfaces:
Graph<V>
public class AdjacencyListGraph<V> extends Object implements Graph<V>
An implementation of the Graph interface that uses an adjacency list to represent the graph.
